Notice is hereby given in terms of Land Use Regulation Act 15 of 1985 together with the Spatial Planning and Land Use Management Act 16 of 2013 for Municipal approval for the proposed Subdivision of Remainder of Erf 905, Fort Beaufort into 2 portions. Copies of the proposed development documentation will be available for inspection at the Municipal Town Planning offices during normal office hours. Any objections must be lodged in writing to the Municipal Manager of Raymond Mhlaba Local Municipality at 8 Somerset Road, Fort Beaufort within 30 days of this notice. All technical inquiries must be directed to the project manager, Mr. Elfranco Britz (ebritz@raymondmhlaba.gov.za / (046) 645-7437) at the Municipal Managers offices. Applicant: Urban Dynamics EC Inc.